original: Lahne, Valdemar, folkskolinspektör, Norrköping, f. 3/9/90 i Övre Ullerud, Värml. 1. G. 26 m. Rut Henrietta Svensson. Barn: Rut f. 26, Lars 28. — Fil. lic. Vik. folksk :lär. i Landskrona 12-13, i Sundsvall 14, vik. samt e. o. i Malmö 15-18, ord. 18-22 o. 26-27, folksk :insp. i Södertälje 27-3’l, därefter komm. folksk :insp. i Norrköp., rektor där 29-31. Kassaförv. i Norrköp. arb:stugor sed. 33, led. av styr. o. insp, f. Manilla dövstumsk. 35-38, led. av styr. f. De dövas väl 36-40, ordf. i Norrköp. tj :mannasällsk. o. i Värml :-gillet i Norrköp. Skr.: Den psyk. ut-veckl. h. gossar i åldern 7-12 år ni. m. RFinlLOlkl, FinlRKSM, FBMM.
translated: Lahne, Valdemar, public school inspector, Norrköping, b. 3/9/90 in Övre Ullerud, Värmland. 1. Married 26 with Rut Henrietta Svensson. Children: Rut b. 26, Lars b. 28. - Bachelor of Philosophy. Temporary public school teacher in Landskrona 12-13, in Sundsvall 14, temporary and then acting in Malmö 15-18, regular from 18-22 and 26-27, public school inspector in Södertälje 27-31, thereafter municipal public school inspector in Norrköping, principal there 29-31. Treasurer in Norrköping labor cottages since 33, board member and inspector for Manilla Deaf-Mute School 35-38, board member for Deaf Welfare Association 36-40, chairman of Norrköping Civil Servants Association and Värmland Guild in Norrköping. Writings: The psychological development of boys aged 7-12. Decorations: Royal Finnish Order of the Lion 1st class, Finnish Red Cross Order of Merit, Freemason Order of the Temple.
